#: matches/services/advanced_stats.py:388
#, python-format
msgid ""
"%(home_team)s has a %(win_pct)s%% win rate playing at home (scoring an "
"average of %(avg_gf)s goals). Their attack is considered %(home_atk)s and "
"defense %(home_def)s. On the other hand, %(away_team)s as the away team wins "
"%(away_win_pct)s%% of their matches, with an %(away_atk)s attack. "
"Statistically, this matchup has a %(over_15)s%% chance of hitting Over 1.5 "
"and a %(btts)s%% chance of Both Teams to Score (BTTS)."
msgstr ""
"O %(home_team)s tiene una tasa de victoria del %(win_pct)s%% jugando en casa "
"(marcando un promedio de %(avg_gf)s goles). Su ataque es considerado "
"%(home_atk)s y su defensa %(home_def)s. Por otro lado, el %(away_team)s como "
"visitante vence el %(away_win_pct)s%% de sus partidos, con un ataque "
"%(away_atk)s. Estadísticamente, este enfrentamiento tiene un %(over_15)s%% "
"de probabilidad de Over 1.5 y un %(btts)s%% de probabilidad de Ambos Marcan "
"(BTTS)."

