#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:413
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This game has a <strong>Base of %(base)s corners</strong>, indicating high "
"offensive volume. With an Over 8.5 prob. at %(prob)s%%, the scenario is "
"ideal for seeking \"Over 8.5 or 9.5\" corner markets."
msgstr "Este partido presenta una <strong>Base de %(base)s córners</strong>, indicando alto volumen ofensivo. Con la Prob. Over 8.5 en %(prob)s%%, el escenario es ideal para buscar mercados de \"Más de 8.5 o 9.5\" córners."

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:417
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The base of %(base)s suggests moderate volume. The best strategy here is to "
"look for safety markets like \"Over 7.5\" or wait for \"Live\" for better "
"odds."
msgstr "La base de %(base)s sugiere un volumen moderado. La mejor estrategia aquí es buscar mercados seguros como \"Over 7.5\" o esperar al \"En Vivo\" para mejores cuotas."

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:421
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Game with a tendency for low lateral volume (Base %(base)s). Be cautious "
"with Over bets; the \"Under\" market or specific corners by time may be more "
"profitable."
msgstr "Partido con tendencia de bajo volumen lateral (Base %(base)s). Tenga cautela con apuestas de Over; el mercado de \"Under\" o córners específicos por tiempo puede ser más rentable."

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:434
msgid "DISCIPLINE (AVERAGE)"
msgstr "DISCIPLINA (PROMEDIO)"

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:441
msgid "Fouls"
msgstr "Faltas"

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:450
msgid "Red Cards Avg:"
msgstr "Promedio de Tarjetas Rojas:"

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:450
msgid "per game"
msgstr "por partido"

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:455
msgid "Insufficient disciplinary data"
msgstr "Datos disciplinarios insuficientes"

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:463
msgid "Disciplinary Tip"
msgstr "Consejo Disciplinario"

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:468
#, python-format
msgid ""
"With an average of <strong>%(fouls)s fouls</strong>, we expect a tense game "
"with many stops. The chance of cards (currently %(cards)s yellows/game) is "
"high."
msgstr "Con un promedio de <strong>%(fouls)s faltas</strong>, esperamos un partido tenso y con muchas interrupciones. La probabilidad de tarjetas (actualmente %(cards)s amarillas/partido) es elevada."

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:472
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Game with a tendency to be more fluid (only %(fouls)s fouls on average). The "
"\"Under Cards\" or \"Less than 4.5\" market could be a good choice if the "
"referee is not strict."
msgstr "Partido con tendencia a ser más fluido (solo %(fouls)s faltas de promedio). El mercado de \"Under Tarjetas\" o \"Menos de 4.5\" puede ser buena opción si el árbitro no es estricto."

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:485
msgid "ATTACK EFFICIENCY"
msgstr "EFICIENCIA DE ATAQUE"

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:491
msgid "Shot Accuracy (Target)"
msgstr "Precisión de Tiro (al Arco)"

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:510
msgid "Shots per Goal"
msgstr "Tiros por Gol"

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:520
msgid "Shot statistics unavailable"
msgstr "Estadísticas de tiro no disponibles"

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:528
msgid "Efficiency Guide"
msgstr "Guía de Eficiencia"

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:532
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Both teams have accuracy above 30%% on target. This is a very strong signal "
"for the <strong>\"Both Teams to Score: Yes\"</strong> or \"Over 1.5/2.5 "
"Goals\" market."
msgstr "Ambos equipos tienen precisión superior al 30%% al arco. Esta es una señal fortísima para el mercado de <strong>\"Ambos Marcan: Sí\"</strong> o \"Over 1.5/2.5 Gols\"."

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:536
msgid ""
"Only one of the teams is being lethal in finishing. Consider betting on the "
"\"Team Goals\" market for the one with higher accuracy."
msgstr "Solo uno de los equipos está siendo letal en las finalizaciones. Considere apostar en el mercado de \"Goles del Equipo\" para el que tenga mayor precisión."

#: matches/templates/matches/match_detail.html:540
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Both teams are struggling with finishing (Accuracy below 30%%). Game with a "
"tendency for few goals, ideal for analyzing the \"Under\" market."
msgstr "Ambos equipos están fallando en la definición (Precisión por debajo del 30%%). Partido con tendencia a pocos goles, ideal para analizar el mercado de \"Under\"."

